data.description: Seller is in the process of installing a kitchenette downstairs so that the property has two separate living spaces* Multi-Generational and Rental Location opportunity! Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Portland! This recently updated 3-bed, 2-bath residence on a spacious .15-acre lot offers an incredible lifestyle. Step inside to a distinctive layout across three organized levels. Main floor features an inviting living area and a well-appointed kitchen with modern appliances, ample storage, and breathtaking views. Upstairs, find the luxurious primary bedroom with a private bathroom and soaring ceilings. The lower level features 2 private bedrooms with dedicated private entryways, opening out to a back deck oasis. This property's standout feature is current cashflow as a lucrative short-term rental, allowing you to live where you profit. Outside, enjoy the private .15-acre lot, multilevel Deck, and covered Hot tub for outdoor activities and relaxation. Conveniently located around trendy shops, restaurants, and transportation. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own in Portland? Schedule a showing today and experience the endless potential of this home -- Don't sleep on this opportunity!
